Project: Two-Wheeled Self-Balancing Robot  
Design Version: v1.3  
Date: 16 July 2025

Key Specs:
- Max Load: 1.5kg
- Motors: 130 RPM DC gear motors
- Sensor: MPU6050 for tilt detection
- Controller: Arduino Nano
- Control Algorithm: PID
- Battery: 6V x2 (Connected in series for combined voltage)
- Size: 10x15x20cm
Constraints:
- Must balance within ±5° tilt
- Must balance for a minimum of 20 seconds without falling
